body:
Hello, I am the Team Manager of Vulcore, known as Nutella Fella.

We are currently looking for a TOP and JG to play for our main roster.

Requirements:
Plat 5 or Higher.
Available afternoons and/or evenings at least 2 days of the week.
None/Low toxicity.
Communication etiquette.

For details on Auspicious Gaming organisation go to [here](https://www.auspiciousgaming.com).
